title: $:/plugins/orange/mermaid-tw5/readme

This is a TiddlyWiki plugin for using [[mermaid.js|https://github.com/mermaid-js/mermaid]]. It is completely self-contained and doesn't need an Internet connection to work. It works both in the browser and under Node.js. It is currently based on [[mermaid.js 11.14.0|https://github.com/mermaid-js/mermaid/releases/tag/v11.14.0]].

Mermaid is lazy-loaded: the library only initialises when a page actually contains a diagram, so pages without diagrams pay no loading cost.

!Installation

You can drag the plugin link into your TiddlyWiki to install, from https://asophila.github.io/mermaid-tw5

!Info

The Mermaid TW5 Plugin is based on:

* https://github.com/asophila/mermaid-tw5
* http://github.com/gt6796c/mermaid-tw5
